	(36855, 15, 0, 'This charade has gone on long enough!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16872, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_BERSERK', 38128),
	(36855, 16, 0, 'All part of the Master\'s plan.... Your end is inevitable....', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16871, 'Lady Deathwhisper - SAY_DEATH', 38125),
	(37007, 0, 0, 'The master\'s sanctum has been disturbed!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16865, 'Deathbound Ward - SAY_TRAP_ACTIVATE', 37443),
	(37007, 0, 1, 'I... awaken!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16866, 'Deathbound Ward - SAY_TRAP_ACTIVATE', 38517),
	(37007, 0, 2, 'Who... goes there...?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16867, 'Deathbound Ward - SAY_TRAP_ACTIVATE', 38518),
	(37108, 0, 0, 'Da spirits be angry with us.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Shi\'kala 1st sentence', 36962),
	(37108, 1, 0, 'I don\' know why the spirits be rejectin\' us so.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Shi\'kala 2nd sentence', 36958),
	(37108, 2, 0, 'Don\' worry, child. Grik\'nir gonna help us get through this.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Shi\'kala 3rd sentence', 0),
	(37119, 0, 0, 'This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people.$B$BRemember, hero, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16653, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_1', 36923),
	(37119, 1, 0, 'Remember, heroes, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16654, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_2', 37028),
	(37119, 2, 0, 'Our march upon Icecrown Citadel begins now!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16655, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_3', 37029),
	(37119, 3, 0, 'ARTHAS! I swore that I would see you dead and the Scourge dismantled! I\'m going to finish what I started at Light\'s Hope!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16656, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_4', 37031),
	(37119, 4, 0, 'The power of the Light knows no bounds, Saurfang. His soul is under great strain, but he lives - for now.', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 16658, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_5', 37056),
	(37119, 5, 0, 'By the Light, it must be so!', 12, 0, 0, 5, 0, 16657, 'Highlord Tirion Fordring - SAY_TIRION_INTRO_A_5', 37038),
	(37122, 0, 0, 'Never... could reach... the top shelf...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16586, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_DEATH', 37074),
	(37122, 1, 0, 'You miserable fools never did manage to select a decent bat wing.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16587, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_RESURRECTED', 37076),
	(37122, 2, 0, 'THAT was for bringing me spoiled spider ichor!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16588, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_KILL', 37075),
	(37122, 3, 0, 'Don\'t... let Finklestein use me... for his potions...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16589, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_SECOND_DEATH', 37077),
	(37122, 4, 0, 'The loss of our comrades was unpreventable. They lived and died in the service of the Argent Crusade.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16590, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_SURVIVE_TALK', 37534),
	(37122, 5, 0, 'Even dying here beats spending another day collecting reagents for that madman, Finklestein. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16585, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_INTRO_2', 36948),
	(37123, 0, 0, 'No amount of healing can save me now. Fight on, brothers...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16810, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_DEATH', 37665),
	(37123, 1, 0, 'What? This strength...? All of the pain is gone! You... must join me in the eternal embrace of death!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16811, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_RESURRECTED', 37664),
	(37123, 2, 0, 'It doesn\'t hurt anymore, does it?\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16812, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_KILL', 37658),
	(37123, 3, 0, 'I\'m sorry...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16813, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_SECOND_DEATH', 37659),
	(37123, 4, 0, 'You have done much in this war against the Scourge. May the light embrace you. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16815, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_SURVIVE_TALK', 37533),
	(37124, 0, 0, 'Please... burn my remains. Let me live warm in the afterlife...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16844, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_DEATH', 37666),
	(37124, 1, 0, 'No! Why was I denied a death by flame? You must all BURN!  ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16845, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_RESURRECTED', 37667),
	(37124, 2, 0, 'Can you feel the burn?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16846, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_KILL', 37660),
	(37124, 3, 0, 'What... have I done? No!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16847, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_SECOND_DEATH', 37661),
	(37124, 4, 0, 'What can possibly redeem this unholy place? Thank you.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16849, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_SURVIVE_TALK', 37535),
	(37125, 0, 0, 'It was... a worthy afterlife.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16998, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_DEATH', 37668),
	(37125, 1, 0, 'There is no escaping the Lich King\'s will. Prepare for an explosive encounter!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16999, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_RESURRECTED', 37669),
	(37125, 2, 0, 'So that\'s what happens what you stand too close to a bomb!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17000, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_KILL', 37662),
	(37125, 3, 0, 'What an... explosive ending!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17001, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_SECOND_DEATH', 37663),
	(37125, 4, 0, 'Beware the dangers that lie ahead... and do try to remain in one piece. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17003, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_SURVIVE_TALK', 37536),
	(37126, 0, 0, 'You may have once fought beside me, Crok, but now you are nothing more than a traitor. Come, your second death approaches!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17017, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_EVENT_START', 37024),
	(37126, 1, 0, 'Miserable creatures! Die! ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17018, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_KILL_CAPTAIN', 37065),
	(37126, 2, 0, 'Foolish Crok. You brought my reinforcements with you. Arise, Argent Champions, and serve the Lich King in death!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17019, 'Sister Svanlna - SAY_RESURRECT_CAPTAINS', 37020),
	(37126, 3, 0, 'Come, Scourgebane. I\'ll show the master which of us is truly worthy of the title of "Champion"!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17020, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_AGGRO', 37653),
	(37126, 4, 0, 'What a pitiful choice of an ally, Crok!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17021, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_KILL', 37654),
	(37126, 5, 0, 'They died so easily. No matter.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17022, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_CAPTAIN_DEATH', 37163),
	(37126, 6, 0, 'Perhaps... you were right, Crok. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17023, 'Sister Svalna - SAY_DEATH', 37135),
	(37126, 7, 0, '%s has impaled $n!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sister Svalna - EMOTE_SVALNA_IMPALE', 37977),
	(37126, 8, 0, '%s\'s Aether Shield has been shattered by $n!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Sister Svalna - EMOTE_SVALNA_BROKEN_SHIELD', 37978),
	(37129, 0, 0, 'Ready your arms, my Argent Brothers. The Vrykul will protect the Frost Queen with their lives.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16819, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_INTRO_1', 36945),
	(37129, 1, 0, 'Enough idle banter! Our champions have arrived - support them as we push our way through the hall!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16820, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_INTRO_3', 36946),
	(37129, 2, 0, 'Draw them back to us, and we\'ll assist you. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16821, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_COMBAT_WP_0', 37013),
	(37129, 3, 0, 'Quickly, push on!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16823, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_COMBAT_WP_1', 37015),
	(37129, 4, 0, 'Her reinforcements will arrive shortly, we must bring her down quickly!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16824, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_FINAL_WP', 37016),
	(37129, 5, 0, 'I\'ll draw her attacks. Return our brothers to their graves, then help me bring her down!', 14, 0, 0, 15, 0, 16825, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_COMBAT_SVALNA', 37017),
	(37129, 6, 0, 'Augh! I must rest for a moment. \n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16826, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_GAUNTLET', 37164),
	(37129, 7, 0, 'Champions! I cannot hold her back any longer.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16827, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_SVALNA', 37165),
	(37129, 8, 0, 'Vengeance alone... was not enough!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16828, 'Crok Scourgebane - SAY_CROK_DEATH', 0),
	(37173, 0, 0, 'What we gon\' do now, you ask ? We wait.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Rikkari 1st sentence', 0),
	(37173, 1, 0, 'Grik\'nir says he gon\' talk to the elemental, get it to fight on our side.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Rikkari 2nd sentence', 36960),
	(37173, 2, 0, 'Soon enough we take over dis valley. Soon enough.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Rikkari 3rd sentence', 0),
	(37174, 0, 0, 'Our land be a land of ice an\' snow', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Mirim\'koa 1st sentence', 0),
	(37174, 1, 0, 'But beneath the earth, child, there always be fire.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Mirim\'koa 2nd sentence', 36964),
	(37174, 2, 0, 'De spirit come from deep down to talk with Grik\'nir.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 3, 0, 'Soothsayer Mirim\'koa 3rd sentence', 36965),
	(37181, 0, 0, 'You now stand upon the hallowed ground of the Scourge. The Light won\'t protect you here, paladin. Nothing will protect you...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17230, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_1', 38054),
	(37181, 1, 0, 'You could have been my greatest champion, Fordring: A force of darkness that would wash over this world and deliver it into a new age of strife.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17231, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_2', 38055),
	(37181, 2, 0, 'But that honor is no longer yours. Soon, I will have a new champion. ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17232, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_3', 38056),
	(37181, 3, 0, 'The breaking of this one has been taxing. The atrocities I have committed upon his soul. He has resisted for so long, but he will bow down before his king soon.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17233, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_4', 37034),
	(37181, 4, 0, 'In the end, you will all serve me.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17234, 'The Lich King - SAY_LK_INTRO_5', 38059),
	(37183, 0, 0, 'NEVER! I... I will never... serve... you...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17078, 'Highlord Bolvar Fordragon - SAY_BOLVAR_INTRO_1', 37035),
	(37187, 0, 0, 'Kor\'kron, move out! Champions, watch your backs. The Scourge have been...', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 17103, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_1', 37634),
	(37187, 1, 0, 'My boy died at the Wrath Gate. I am here only to collect his body.', 12, 0, 0, 397, 0, 17097, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_3', 37638),
	(37187, 2, 0, 'We named him Dranosh - It means "Heart of Draenor" in orcish. I would not let the warlocks take him. My boy would be safe, hidden away by the elders of Garadar.', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 17098, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_5', 37640),
	(37187, 3, 0, 'I made a promise to his mother before she died; that I would cross the Dark Portal alone - whether I lived or died, my son would be safe. Untainted...', 12, 0, 0, 1, 0, 17099, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_6', 37641),
	(37187, 4, 0, 'Today, I fulfill that promise.', 12, 0, 0, 397, 0, 17100, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_7', 37642),
	(37187, 5, 0, '%s charges!', 16, 0, 0, 53, 0, 17104, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_8', 37643),
	(37187, 6, 0, 'Behind you lies the body of my only son. Nothing will keep me from him. ', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17094, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_8', 37525),
	(37187, 7, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang walks over to his son and kneels before his son\'s body.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_12', 0),
	(37187, 8, 0, '[Orcish] No\'ku kil zil\'nok ha tar.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17096, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_13', 0),
	(37187, 9, 0, 'Higher Overlord Saurfang picks up the body of his son and walks over towards Varian', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_14', 0),
	(37187, 10, 0, 'I will not forget this... kindness. I thank you, Highness', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17095, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_15', 37529),
	(37187, 11, 0, '%s coughs.', 16, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17105, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_1', 37646),
	(37187, 12, 0, '%s weeps over the corpse of his son.', 16, 0, 0, 15, 0, 17106, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_2', 37647),
	(37187, 13, 0, 'You will have a proper ceremony in Nagrand, next to the pyres of your mother and ancestors.\n', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17101, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_3', 37648),
	(37187, 14, 0, 'Honor, young heroes... no matter how dire the battle... never forsake it.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17102, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_OUTRO_HORDE_4', 37649),
	(37187, 15, 0, 'The paladin still lives? Is it possible, Highlord? Could he have survived?', 12, 0, 0, 6, 0, 17107, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_1', 37051),
	(37187, 16, 0, 'Then we must save him! If we rescue Bolvar Fordragon, we may quell the unrest between the Alliance and the Horde.', 12, 0, 0, 5, 0, 17108, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2', 37053),
	(37187, 17, 0, 'Our mission is now clear: The Lich King will answer for his crimes and we will save Highlord Bolvar Fordragon!', 12, 0, 0, 15, 0, 17109, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3', 37054),
	(37187, 18, 0, 'Kor\'kron, prepare Orgrim\'s Hammer for its final voyage! Champions, our gunship will find a point to dock on the upper reaches of the citadel. Meet us there!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 17110, 'High Overlord Saurfang - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4', 37055),
	(37188, 0, 0, '%s cries.', 12, 0, 0, 18, 0, 16651, 'Lady Jaina Proudmoore - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_17', 29772),
	(37188, 1, 0, 'It was nothing, your majesty. Just... I\'m proud of my king.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16652, 'Lady Jaina Proudmoore - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_19', 37546),
	(37200, 0, 0, 'Let\'s get a move on then! Move ou...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16974, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_1', 37457),
	(37200, 1, 0, 'A lone orc against the might of the Alliance???', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16970, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_4', 37460),
	(37200, 2, 0, 'Charge!!!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16971, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_5', 37461),
	(37200, 3, 0, '%s gasps for air.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16975, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_1', 37502),
	(37200, 4, 0, 'That was Saurfang\'s boy - the Horde commander at the Wrath Gate. Such a tragic end...', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16976, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_2', 37503),
	(37200, 5, 0, 'What in the... There, in the distance!\n', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16977, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_3', 37504),
	(37200, 6, 0, 'A Horde Zeppelin flies up to the rise.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_4', 0),
	(37200, 7, 0, 'Soldiers, fall in! Looks like the Horde are comin\' to take another shot!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16978, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_5', 37505),
	(37200, 8, 0, 'The Zeppelin docks, and High Overlord Saurfang hops out, confronting the Alliance soldiers and Muradin', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_6', 0),
	(37200, 9, 0, 'Don\'t force me hand, orc. We can\'t let ye pass.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16972, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_7', 37524),
	(37200, 10, 0, 'I... I can\'t do it. Get back on yer ship and we\'ll spare yer life. ', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16973, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_9', 37526),
	(37200, 11, 0, 'A mage portal from Stormwind appears between the two and Varian Wrynn and Jaina Proudmoore emerge.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_10', 0),
	(37200, 12, 0, 'Right away, yer majesty!', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16979, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_OUTRO_ALLIANCE_21', 37547),
	(37200, 13, 0, 'Could it be, Lord Fordring? If Bolvar lives, mayhap there is hope fer peace between the Alliance and the Horde. We must reach the top o\' this cursed place and free the paladin!', 12, 0, 0, 6, 0, 16980, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2', 37037),
	(37200, 14, 0, 'Prepare the Skybreaker fer an aerial assault on the citadel!', 14, 0, 0, 5, 0, 16981, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3', 37043),
	(37200, 15, 0, 'Heroes, ye must fight yer way to a clear extraction point within Icecrown. We\'ll try an\' rendezvous on the ramparts!', 14, 0, 0, 22, 0, 16982, 'Muradin Bronzebeard - SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4', 37046),
	(37217, 0, 0, '%s cries out with a loud, baying howl!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Precious - EMOTE_PRECIOUS_ZOMBIES', 37849),
	(37491, 1, 0, 'You miserable fools never did manage to select a decent bat wing.', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16587, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_RESURRECTED', 37076),
	(37491, 2, 0, 'THAT was for bringing me spoiled spider ichor!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16588, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_KILL', 37075),
	(37491, 3, 0, 'Don\'t... let Finklestein use me... for his potions...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16589, 'Captain Arnath - SAY_ARNATH_SECOND_DEATH', 37077),
	(37493, 1, 0, 'What? This strength...? All of the pain is gone! You... must join me in the eternal embrace of death!\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16811, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_RESURRECTED', 37664),
	(37493, 2, 0, 'It doesn\'t hurt anymore, does it?\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16812, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_KILL', 37658),
	(37493, 3, 0, 'I\'m sorry...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16813, 'Captain Brandon - SAY_BRANDON_SECOND_DEATH', 37659),
	(37494, 1, 0, 'No! Why was I denied a death by flame? You must all BURN!  ', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16845, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_RESURRECTED', 37667),
	(37494, 2, 0, 'Can you feel the burn?', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16846, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_KILL', 37660),
	(37494, 3, 0, 'What... have I done? No!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16847, 'Captain Grondel - SAY_GRONDEL_SECOND_DEATH', 37661),
	(37495, 1, 0, 'There is no escaping the Lich King\'s will. Prepare for an explosive encounter!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16999, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_RESURRECTED', 37669),
	(37495, 2, 0, 'So that\'s what happens what you stand too close to a bomb!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17000, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_KILL', 37662),
	(37495, 3, 0, 'What an... explosive ending!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 17001, 'Captain Rupert - SAY_RUPERT_SECOND_DEATH', 37663),
	(37813, 0, 0, 'For every Horde soldier that you killed -- for every Alliance dog that fell, the Lich King\'s armies grew. Even now the val\'kyr work to raise your fallen as Scourge.\n', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16701, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_2', 37458),
	(37813, 1, 0, 'Things are about to get much worse. Come, taste the power that the Lich King has bestowed upon me!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16702, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_3', 37459),
	(37813, 2, 0, 'Dwarves...', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16703, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_6', 37471),
	(37813, 3, 0, '%s immobilizes Muradin and his guards.', 12, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_ALLIANCE_7', 0),
	(37813, 4, 0, 'Join me, father. Join me and we will crush this world in the name of the Scourge -- for the glory of the Lich King!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16704, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_2', 37635),
	(37813, 5, 0, 'Stubborn and old. What chance do you have? I am stronger, and more powerful than you ever were.', 14, 0, 0, 5, 0, 16705, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_4', 37639),
	(37813, 6, 0, 'Pathetic old orc! Come then, heroes. Come and face the might of the Scourge!', 14, 0, 0, 15, 0, 16706, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_INTRO_HORDE_9', 37644),
	(37813, 7, 0, 'BY THE MIGHT OF THE LICH KING!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16694, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_AGGRO', 38464),
	(37813, 8, 0, 'The ground runs red with your blood!', 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 16699, 'Deathbringer Saurfang - SAY_MARK_OF_THE_FALLEN_CHAMPION', 37995),
