	(29068, 27, 0, 'A pact was made, $g brother:sister;! We vowed vengeance against the Lich King! For what he had done to us! We battled the Scourge as Forsaken, pushing them back into the Plaguelands and freeing Tirisifal! You and I were champions of the Forsaken!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_THINK_1', 29398),
	(29068, 26, 0, 'You don\'t remember me, mon? Damn da Scourge! Dey gone ta drain you of everytin\' dat made ya a mojo masta. Every last ounce a good... Everytin\' dat made ya a troll hero, mon!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_NOREM_9', 29407),
