	(25162, 4, 0, 'Now that that\'s out of the way, welcome to the Isle of Quel\'Danas. The Sunwell\'s on the plateau to the south, and Prince Kael\'thas is holed up in the Magisters\' Terrace to the east.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum', 24213),
