	(25162, 10, 0, 'I know, we thought he was dead too, but that\'s not the case. He\'s trying to use the Sunwell to bring the master of the Burning Legion, Kil\'Jaeden, into this world.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum', 24218),
	(25162, 11, 0, 'Let me assure you people that if he\'s successful, this world will suffer far worse than Outland ever did! So, let\'s make sure that doesn\'t come to pass.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum', 24219),
	(25162, 12, 0, 'Warriors will be deployed to hold key positions, while you marksmen will be assigned to keep the enemy fliers at bay.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Drill Sergeant Bahduum', 24220),
