	(11832, 0, 0, 'We will locate the origin of the Nightmare through the fragments you collected, $n. From there we will pull Eranikus through a rift in the Dream. Steel yourself, $c. We are inviting the embodiment of the Nightmare into our world.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 0', 11282),
	(11832, 1, 1, 'The rift will be opened there, above Lake Elun\'ara. Prepare yourself, $n. Eranikus\'s entry into our world will be wrought with chaos and strife.\n', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 1', 11290),
	(11832, 2, 2, 'He will stop at nothing to get to Malfurion\'s physical manifestation. That must not happen... We must keep the beast occupied long enough for Tyrande to arrive.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 2', 11291),
	(11832, 3, 3, 'Defend Nighthaven, hero...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 3', 11292),
	(11832, 4, 4, 'Fiend! Face the might of Cenarius!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 4', 11293),
	(11832, 5, 5, 'Who is the predictable one, beast? Surely you did not think that we would summon you on top of Malfurion? Your redemption comes, Eranikus. You will be cleansed of this madness - this corruption.\n', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 4', 11295),
	(11832, 6, 6, 'Hurry, $n! We must find protective cover!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 6', 11300),
	(11832, 7, 7, 'Please, champion, protect our people.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 7', 11301),
	(11832, 8, 8, 'It will be done, Eranikus. Be well, ancient one.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 8', 11303),
	(11832, 9, 9, 'Let us leave Nighthaven, hero. Seek me out at the grove.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos Say 9', 11329),
	(11832, 10, 10, 'Come, $n. The lake is just around the bend.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 0', 10866),
	(11832, 11, 11, 'Stand near me, $n. I will protect you should anything go wrong.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 1', 10867),
	(11832, 12, 12, 'Malfurion!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 2', 10868),
	(11832, 13, 13, 'It was shrouded in nightmares, Malfurion. What is happening in the Dream? What could cause such atrocities?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 3', 10870),
	(11832, 14, 14, 'I sensed as much, Malfurion. Dark days loom ahead.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 4', 10872),
	(11832, 15, 15, 'You have been gone too long, Malfurion. Peace between the children of Azeroth is tenuous at best. What of my father? Of your brother? Have you any news?\n', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 5', 10874),
	(11832, 16, 16, 'Farewell, old friend... Farewell...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 6', 10877),
	(11832, 17, 17, 'Let us return to the grove, mortal.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Keeper Remulos - say Text 7', 10879),
	(15491, 0, 0, 'Pitiful, predictable mortals... You know not what you have done! The Master\'s will fulfilled. The Moonglade shall be destroyed and Malfurion along with it!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 0', 11030),
	(15491, 1, 1, '%s lets loose a sinister laugh.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 1', 11296),
	(15491, 2, 2, 'You are certainly not your father, insect. Should it interest me, I would crush you with but a swipe of my claws. Turn Shan\'do Stormrage over to me and your pitiful life will be spared along with the lives of your people.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 2', 11294),
	(15491, 3, 3, 'My redemption? You are bold, little one. My redemption comes by the will of my god.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 3', 11297),
	(15491, 4, 4, '%s roars furiously.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 4', 11298),
	(15491, 5, 5, 'Rise, servants of the Nightmare! Rise and destroy this world! Let there be no survivors...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 5', 11299),
	(15491, 6, 6, 'Where is your savior? How long can you hold out against my attacks? ', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 6', 11304),
	(15491, 7, 7, 'Remulos, look how easy they fall before me? You can stop this, fool. Turn the druid over to me and it will all be over...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 7', 11306),
	(15491, 8, 8, 'Defeated my minions? Then face me, mortals!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 8', 11305),
	(15491, 9, 9, 'IT BURNS! THE PAIN... SEARING...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 9', 11314),
	(15491, 10, 10, 'WHY? Why did this happen to ... to me? Where were you Tyrande? Where were you when I fell from the grace of Elune?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 10', 11315),
	(15491, 11, 11, 'I... I feel... I feel the touch of Elune upon my being once more... She smiles upon me... Yes... I...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 11', 11316),
	(15491, 12, 12, '%s falls to one knee.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus Say 12', 11319),
	(15633, 0, 0, 'Seek absolution, Eranikus. All will be forgiven...\n', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Tyrande Say 0', 11310),
	(15633, 1, 1, 'You will be forgiven, Eranikus. Elune will always love you. Break free of the bonds that command you!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Tyrande Say 0', 11311),
	(15633, 2, 2, 'The grasp of the Old Gods is unmoving. He is consumed by their dark thoughts... I... I cannot... cannot channel much longer... Elune aid me...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Tyrande Say 0', 11312),
	(15628, 0, 0, 'For so long, I was lost... The Nightmare\'s corruption had consumed me... And now, you... all of you... you have saved me. Released me from its grasp.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus the Redeemed Say 0', 11323),
	(15628, 1, 1, 'But... Malfurion, Cenarius, Ysera... they still fight. They need me. I must return to the Dream at once.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus the Redeemed Say 0', 11324),
	(15628, 2, 2, 'My lady, I am unworthy of your prayer. Truly, you are an angel of light. Please, assist me in returning to the barrow den so that I may return to the Dream. I, like Malfurion, also have a love awaiting me... I must return to her... to protect her...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus the Redeemed Say 0', 11326),
	(15628, 3, 3, 'And heroes... I hold that which you seek. May it once more see the evil dissolved. Remulos, see to it that our champion receives the shard of the Green Flight.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Eranikus the Redeemed Say 0', 11327),
	(15629, 0, 0, '%s drinks in the suffering of the fallen.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Nightmare Phantasm Say 0', 11289),
	(17949, 0, 0, 'Remulos, old friend. It is good to see you once more. I knew that the message would find its way to you - one way or another.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Malfurion Stormrage - say Text 0', 10869),
	(17949, 1, 0, 'I fear for the worst, old friend. Within the Dream we fight a new foe, born of an ancient evil. Ysera\'s noble brood has fallen victim to the old whisperings. It seems as if the Nightmare has broken through the realm and seeks a new host on Azeroth.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Malfurion Stormrage - say Text 1', 10871),
	(17949, 2, 0, 'Aye, Remulos. Prepare the mortal races.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Malfurion Stormrage - say Text 2', 10873),
	(17949, 3, 0, 'Cenarius fights at my side. Illidan sits atop his throne in the Outland - brooding. I am afraid that the loss to Arthas proved to be his breaking point. Madness has embraced him, Remulos. He replays the events in his mind a thousand times per day, but in his mind, he is the victor and Arthas is utterly defeated. He is too far gone, old friend. I fear that the time may soon come that our bond is tested and it will not be as it was at the Well in Zin-Azshari. ', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Malfurion Stormrage - say Text 3', 10876),
	(17949, 4, 0, 'Remulos, I am being drawn back... Tyrande... send her my love... Tell her I am safe. Tell her... Tell her I will return... Farewell...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Malfurion Stormrage - say Text 4', 10878),
	(32149, 0, 0, 'It was awful... I dreamt I was fighting against my friends.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Fallen Hero\'s Spirit', 35293),
	(32149, 0, 1, 'I\'m so tired. Just let me rest for a moment.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Fallen Hero\'s Spirit', 35295),
	(32149, 0, 2, 'I can\'t hear the screams anymore. Is this the end?', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Fallen Hero\'s Spirit', 35294),
	(32149, 0, 3, 'At last... now I can rest.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Fallen Hero\'s Spirit', 35291),
	(32149, 0, 4, 'My nightmare, is it finally over?', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Fallen Hero\'s Spirit', 35292),
	(25751, 5, 0, '%s\'s eyes glow red for a brief moment.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang', 11563),
	(25751, 6, 0, 'Is that the best you can do?', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang', 13130),
	(25751, 7, 0, 'You\'ll make no mention of me. Either of you!', 12, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'High Overlord Saurfang', 24938),
	(26203, 3, 0, 'Do not fail me, San\'layn. Return to Icecrown with this fool\'s head or do not bother to return. ', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 14758, 'Image The Lich King - Say 3', 0),
	(25251, 1, 0, 'I thought... I thought you were... dead.', 14, 0, 100, 5, 0, 14489, 'Leryssa - Say 1', 25843),
	(25251, 2, 0, 'Don\'t leave me again!  You want to fight for your country, but they don\'t even want you!  They sent you here to die!', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 14490, 'Leryssa - Say 2', 25848),
	(25251, 3, 0, 'I know that look in your eye... I\'m not going to be able to talk you out of this.  If you die on me again...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 14491, 'Leryssa - Say 3', 25849),
