	(55488, 0, 0, 'Here\'s what\'s left of the message we found, $n. Can you make any sense of it?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Corastrasza', 54349),
	(56333, 0, 0, 'Let\'s move out, friend! There\'s no time to lose.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text0', 54902),
	(56333, 1, 0, 'Corastrasza is understandably upset. Under her care was the one black dragon egg that we believe was free of the taint of Deathwing\'s corruption...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text1', 54903),
	(56333, 2, 0, '...and it was stolen away from us by thieves in the night!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text2', 54904),
	(56333, 3, 0, 'You\'ve found for us our only lead. The rogues from Ravenholdt are behind this.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text3', 54905),
	(56333, 4, 0, 'Ravenholdt? It just doesn\'t make sense! A mongrel band of petty thieves. How did they even KNOW about the egg?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text4', 54906),
	(56333, 5, 0, 'We\'ll get to the bottom of this. Someone with your skills is exactly what we need.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text5', 54907),
	(56333, 6, 0, 'What\'s the expression? "To catch a thief", they say?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text6', 54908),
	(56333, 7, 0, 'Look at this devastation. These foothills have never recovered from the campaigns of the second and third wars.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text7', 54909),
	(56333, 8, 0, 'Ruins and debris litter the landscape... and I consider the thieves and assassins of Ravenholdt to be part of that debris.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text8', 54910),
	(56333, 9, 0, 'Without a state... without a cause... what drives them, do you wonder?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text9', 54911),
	(56333, 10, 0, 'And what possessed them to strike out against the red dragonflight? Madness. We must learn more!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text10', 54912),
	(56333, 11, 0, 'We\'re almost to Ravenholdt Manor.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text11', 54913),
	(56333, 12, 0, 'If they have the egg, it\'s too dangerous to risk an all-out assault. You\'ll need to sneak in there, find out what they\'re up to... And retrieve the egg at any cost.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz Flight Text12', 54914),
	(56375, 0, 0, 'Stay on the ground, and stay hidden. Ill port you back here if you get into any trouble!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz (Ravenholdt)', 55054),
	(56375, 1, 0, 'Well... That got ugly. You\'re lucky I\'m here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Mostrasz (Ravenholdt)', 55195),
