	(56515, 0, 3, 'I see you, fool!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Ravenholdt Stalker', 55202),
	(58118, 0, 0, 'That\'s right, mortal. The prize you seek no longer sleeps within a shell. Here I am: in the flesh.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text0', 56836),
	(58118, 1, 0, 'I\'m not some trophy for a red dragon\'s mantle-piece, and I\'m never going back.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text1', 56837),
	(58118, 2, 0, 'Don\'t look so surprised! We dragons are conscious, even within our shells. As I grew, I could hear the plotting and scheming. I was to be born a prisoner.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text2', 56838),
	(58118, 3, 0, 'But I\'m one-of-a-kind! A black dragon raised free from the taint of my father\'s corruption. And that\'s how I intend to stay: free.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text3', 56839),
	(58118, 4, 0, 'Somehow, you managed to elude all of my guards. You slipped in here like a ghost. That makes you... valuable to me. Let\'s talk.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text4', 56840),
	(58118, 5, 0, 'You don\'t recognize your former prisoner?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text5', 56841),
	(58118, 6, 0, 'No. I want him to deliver a message to the red dragonflight.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text6', 56842),
	(58118, 7, 0, 'Tell them that I am free of my father\'s madness, and I will be free of them as well. I am to be left alone: this will be my first and only warning.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text7', 56843),
	(58118, 8, 0, 'Deathwing\'s minions should be afraid of ME. Get him out of here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text8', 56844),
	(58118, 9, 0, 'And Fahrad?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text9', 56845),
	(58118, 10, 0, 'Break his legs.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text10', 56846),
	(58118, 11, 0, 'Now then, my new friend. We have much to talk about.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text11', 56847),
	(58118, 12, 0, 'As you know, Black Dragons frequently disguise themselves as humanoids in order to tamper with mortal affairs.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text12', 56447),
	(58118, 13, 0, 'While the house of my mad father collapses around him, the few remaining Black Dragons have gone into hiding.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text13', 56448),
	(58118, 14, 0, 'But I can still sense them. My cowardly brothers and sisters will cause untold suffering if we allow them to stay in the shadows.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text14', 56449),
	(58118, 15, 0, 'Moreover, they are a threat to me.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text15', 56450),
	(58118, 16, 0, 'That\'s where you come in. Help us to slay them all, and I will reward you handsomely.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text16', 56451),
	(58118, 17, 0, 'The dragon you\'re looking for goes by the name Creed.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'Wrathion Text17', 56481),
